<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/fdbcdaa27f824fa78a9af1575b36a019.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3、将瓶子顶端沿图中红色箭头方向剪4道小口，约2㎝长即可。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/16a7378164434cf696cde8c29fc6b509.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4、把一次性杯子装进去。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/88f60ea5caab465190f05d697765d023.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>5、裁下来的瓶底当盖子，盖到底部。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/ed4f105eb3ac4cbfa95a372c03624053.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/1786718a7dd240d4916a5c0b672c3d22.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/1c076ef84d30483ab51ecb9509f5daa7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>6、大功告成！取一个杯子，剩下的杯子会自动到瓶口。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/77c8a256843c454fbb051b464e680473.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/5f1cc5b47fb34ed1aaa584d36aa28f0d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>二、插线板防尘防潮套</p>
<p>1、准备一个空矿泉水瓶子。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/9f42f61ae8ad4cf5a34385a5b6d31b06.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>2、用美工刀裁掉瓶口。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/b40bebf29e70484fb96cefc3f8c0bced.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/9a21c8b39922427b9e617200c6a85d41.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3、把上半部分的锥形裁下来，备用。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/dba95698baf24a0fb84d9a8f3dc62ce8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/cddc3aade717474e83aa1464c0b29f54.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4、沿瓶身纵向开一道0.5㎝的槽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/b7def9f2e124479d88fe328aa3cdf44e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/5e48fd1c47a04ccea5d1a741abe4b818.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/e68199d15d804c968a765f4af5db7ae9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/f6145c71a96142c2b4c69e574224d670.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/a1468ff19fba427fb60375609ba0fb22.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4、把插线板装入瓶内，插头线从槽中出来，然后把槽转到插线板背面。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/920514f3c25b49a3a7c6761e1f6bbd90.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/b3459d93899147eb9863c138d0c9c4e1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>5、之前裁下来的锥形的部分从插线板的插头套进去，扣到瓶身。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/c6e51d3e95574820a5e288eacd542674.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>6、大功告成！不小心落点灰尘，洒点小水啥的基本都能应付。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/607ad362431341f8bc1ebb1fb3fd1bfa.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/fb65a23e4e3042ad93a8c5bacfb28c28.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180910/eaa3dcaaad2d4108a0e856f69b7462a6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
